upgrades.title: Emergency Medicine
upgrades.description: All restoration effects provided by Orb pickups increased by 25%.

upgrades.description: Magnetic Status Effects also pull in enemies within 1m per stack.

upgrades.description: Shoot Health Orbs to pick them up. Health orbs now have 25% chance to duplicate when picked up.

upgrades.description: Non-Tenno Allies within 20m all gain +5% Melee Attack Speed and +20% Fire Rate for each one in range.

deviation.description: Fissures rip into the mission, causing the Enemy Level to go up by 1 every 10s. Destroy them to stop the level from increasing further.

risks.description: Slain enemies burts with Void energy.
